## How to Deploy to Production

Install pre-requisites:

```
$ brew install redis
$ cd /path/to/charted.co
$ npm install
$ cd /path/to/charted
$ npm install
```

Update Charted to the latest version:

```
$ cd /path/to/charted
$ bin/build --prod --plugins=/path/to/charted.co/plugins/
$ cp -r out/ /path/to/charted.co/charted
```

Verify:

```
$ redis-server
$ heroku local web
```

Deploy:

```
$ git push heroku master
```

## Plugins

There are two plugins: `head.html` and `footer.html`. The former
is used to install Google Analytics while the latter is used to
add a privacy link to the footer.
